                          <div style="font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px;">Company Details</div>
                          <div style="color:#374151;">
                            <strong>OEL WORLDWIDE INDUSTRIES</strong><br/><br/>

                            <strong>Physical Address:</strong><br/>
                            OEL Worldwide Ind.<br/>
                            701 County Line Road<br/>
                            Palmer Lake, CO<br/>
                            80133<br/><br/>

                            <strong>Billing Address:</strong><br/>
                            OEL Worldwide Ind.<br/>
                            PO Box 445<br/>
                            Palmer Lake, CO<br/>
                            80133<br/><br/>

                            <strong>Accounting Department / Accounts Payable:</strong><br/>
                            Stacey Cahalane – stacey@oelsales.com<br/>
                            Karol Fisher – Karol@oelsales.com<br/><br/>

                            <strong>Customer Service – Basic questions, tracking, order updates, etc.</strong><br/>
                            customerservice@oelsales.com<br/>
                            719-559-0951 ext. 1<br/><br/>

                            <strong>PO Submission:</strong><br/>
                            orders@oelsales.com<br/><br/>

