                            • W9 Form<br/>
                            • Customer Credit Application – please fill this out and send it back to us<br/>
                            • Latest Pricesheet<br/><br/>

                            <strong>Marketing:</strong><br/>
                            Asa Dyer – asa@oelsales.com
                          </div>
                        </div>

                        <p style="margin:0 0 18px 0;">
                          If there is anything else you need for your records or onboarding process,
                          don’t hesitate to reach out.
                        </p>

                        <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #E5E7EB; margin:16px 0;"/>

                        <div style="color:#6B7280; font-size:12px;">
                          This email was sent from a no-reply address. Please do not reply to this message.
                        </div>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>

                <div style="color:#6B7280; font-size:12px; margin-top:12px;">
                  <div>${object.company_id.name}</div>
                  <div>
                    <t t-esc="object.company_id.phone or ''"/> ·
                    <t t-esc="object.company_id.email or ''"/>
                  </div>
                  <div><t t-esc="object.company_id.website or ''"/></div>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </field>
    </record>

  </data>
</odoo>
